{"tid":2352232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主黨佩洛西第四度當選眾議院議長","createTime":"2021-01-04T01:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T04:38:54.000Z","uid":278587,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"567367d5214e714016cfbaa73fa850cbf3958d06","tid":2352232,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:35:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=418887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418887&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=57037908\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418887&h=29b74fa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=418887</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國國會參眾兩院新一屆議員宣誓就職，民主黨的佩洛西成功連任眾議院議長。<br />\n<br />\n去年十一月大選後，在眾議院僅有過半數優勢的民主黨，成功保住議長之位。<br />\n<br />\n80歲的佩洛西獲得216票支持，僅以7票之差險勝主要對手共和黨眾議院領袖麥卡錫，第四次擔任眾議院議長，她其後主持會議及宣誓儀式。<br />\n<br />\n參議院同日亦會舉行宣誓儀式，共和和民主兩黨目前在參議院分別取得50席及48席，均未能取得過半數，要留待佐治亞州在當地周二重新投票，選出最後的關鍵兩席，才能決定參議院控制權誰屬。"},{"pid":"a71b843d44496ac0763da7ad1f81a50f6f7510be","tid":2352232,"uid":37487,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:36:20.000Z","msg":"連登仔契媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb09cf845b6b456d6fa479d39dff90c13434c7e8","tid":2352232,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a71b843d44496ac0763da7ad1f81a50f6f7510be","tid":2352232,"uid":37487,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:36:20.000Z","msg":"連登仔契媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:54:32.000Z","msg":"你契媽近來露晒底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644d356bc290a8f5e94a0ae828e54fd4cca06e89","tid":2352232,"uid":4722,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021